name: .EXZ File Extension
summary: Learn about .EXZ files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can run the program an EXZ file contains with the EXZ application launcher (Windows). If you want to extract the constituent files an EXZ file contains, rename the file to use the .zip extension and open it as you would any ZIP file.
